    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>亲爱的魔法师们。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到令人兴奋的魔药制作世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吉尼刚刚开了一家魔药店，但面临许多财务挑战。为了维持店铺运营，你需要探索地下城，制作魔药并出售它们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>制作魔药。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043950/extras/5036fd8d2ffc27c7633100114bf8e211.poster.avif?t=1768127751\" width=770 height=434 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043950/extras/5036fd8d2ffc27c7633100114bf8e211.webm?t=1768127751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043950/extras/5036fd8d2ffc27c7633100114bf8e211.mp4?t=1768127751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你必须制作魔药，并与没有魔法能力的魔法师吉尼和小小的月亮鼠洛克塔·休一起管理店铺。（P.S.: 吉尼为了开店向一只无情的猫借了大笔钱。）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>收集魔药材料。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043950/extras/aa5c20dbb0c82e5e06112c0c67d3f486.poster.avif?t=1768127751\" width=766 height=430 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043950/extras/aa5c20dbb0c82e5e06112c0c67d3f486.webm?t=1768127751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043950/extras/aa5c20dbb0c82e5e06112c0c67d3f486.mp4?t=1768127751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >展开冒险以节省材料成本。面对可怕而凶猛的生物，并使用魔药的力量收集材料！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>出售魔药。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043950/extras/a5b5547e4397bbda41b1e77142edefc0.poster.avif?t=1768127751\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043950/extras/a5b5547e4397bbda41b1e77142edefc0.webm?t=1768127751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043950/extras/a5b5547e4397bbda41b1e77142edefc0.mp4?t=1768127751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >了解你的魔法顾客的喜好，并向他们出售魔药。顾客有着不同的品味。随着游戏的进行，他们的信息将被添加到吉尼的日记中。出售符合场合的创意魔药。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在试玩版中可以做什么？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以探索一个地下城（森林），并用从森林收集的材料制作魔药。你还可以向八位魔法顾客出售魔药，并在开头玩主线故事。</p>",
